Class FunctionNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • syntaxtree.SyntaxTreeNode
      • syntaxtree.ExpressionNode
        • syntaxtree.VariableNode
          • syntaxtree.FunctionNode

  • public class FunctionNode
extends VariableNode
    Bob Laskowski, Compilers II, Dr. Erik Steinmetz, April 27th, 2017

    The node for a call to a function. Stores the name and an ArrayList of the arguments.

    Author:
    Bob Laskowski
